# NOTIFICATION_CHAT: Admin/Monitoring Chats
# Purpose: System monitoring, errors, performance metrics
# Format: Comma-separated chat IDs
# Get ID: Message @userinfobot on Telegram
#
# Examples:
#   Single admin: 123456789
